s, but usually three steps better than regular leather and very lightweight, great black leather color too).<br>Imbued Mithril Studded armor (Imbued version: +1-2 WIS, +1-3 CHA, AC comparable to Reinforced).<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Smithed armors</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Banded armor.<br>Ornate Chain (silver, electrum, gold, or platinum).<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Smithed weapons</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Forged weapons.<br>Forged Velium weapons.<br>Mithril Fier'Dal weapons (Imbued versions: +2 WIS +2 CHA +4 AGI).<br>Silvered weapons. <p><center><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~andersonrob/lasgalensig.jpg" border="0"></center><b><center>Lasgalen Lothir</center></b><i><center>Oakheart of the Conclave of the Righteous</center></i><i><center>Warden of Tunare</center></i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubreezeewinterrose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Breezee Winterrose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/27/02 7:55:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=331.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lasgalen's Silk, Leather, and Steel</span><hr size=1> Have been very busy of late in-game and in-RL, so I wasn't able to get back to you for summoning vials of mana.  Also, would be interested in a full suit of ornate gold chain, just let me know how much this will cost me.<br><br><br>Breezee <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/urobingoodfellow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Robin Goodfellow</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 517<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/30/02 3:04:22 am)</font><br> 